Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingAddress": "Calle Ortega y Gasset 4, Madrid, 28001",
  "phone": "666777888",
  "paymentMethod": "STRIPE"
}

### Ver mis pedidos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders

### Ver detalle de un pedido
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### ========================================
### FAVORITOS
### ========================================

### Ver mis favoritos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/favorites

### Añadir producto a favoritos
POST http://localhost:8080/api/favorites/1

### Eliminar de favoritos
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/favorites/1

### Verificar si un producto está en favoritos
GET http://localhost:8080/api/favorites/check/1

### ========================================
### TALLAS Y STOCK
### ========================================

### Ver todas las tallas de un producto
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/sizes

### Ver solo tallas con stock disponible
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/sizes/available

### Ver stock de una talla específica
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/sizes/42

### Actualizar stock de una talla (admin)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/products/1/sizes/42/stock?stock=50

### ========================================
### PAGOS (STRIPE)
### ========================================

### Crear Payment Intent
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/create-intent
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 150.00,
  "currency": "eur"
}

### Verificar estado del pago
GET http://localhost:8080/api/payments/verify/pi_xxxxxxxxxx

### ========================================
### ADMIN - PRODUCTOS
### ========================================

### Crear producto
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nike Air Max 97",
  "brand": "Nike",
  "price": 180.00,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "description": "Zapatillas retro con diseño de onda",
  "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/600"
}

### Actualizar producto
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Chicago' - ACTUALIZADO",
  "brand": "Nike",
  "price": 199.99,
  "categoryId": 1,
  "description": "Edición actualizada",
  "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/600"
}

### Eliminar producto
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/products/31

